Summary: saw after event in photograph, can not identify/explain object
divs: sighting detailswe noticed this two days after the event when uploading photographs from a recent vacation. the image is of my children at niagara falls, and was taken by their sister, on the canadian side. the camera is a vivitar vivicam 9112. we can not identify\explain the object, but we were extremely excited when we noticed it in the photo!
